meta.info: This is the data file for ActiView benchmark that evaluates the active perception abilities for MLLMs. Each instances consist of a question, answer, option list, images path list, question category. Additional keys are: distraction (if the distracting information appears in the image that potentially misleads the mdoel to derive incorrect answers), contains_bbox (if the corresponding splits contain human annotated visual clues). The images are arranged in the following order: original image(not used during evaluation, provided for future research), full image, full image with split lines, upper left split, lower left split, upper right split, lower right split.
meta.note: Make sure you've read the info and are aware of the structure of the image path list before evaluating!!!
meta.authors: Ziyue Wang, Yurui Dong, Fuwen Luo
